---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
import Section from "../components/Section.astro";
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
import CTA from "../components/CTA.astro";
---

<Base
  title="HearthAI — Pereste"
  description="HearthAI is Pereste's first clinical AI solution: an adaptive, voice-based discharge companion for diabetic patients, designed to reduce preventable readmissions."
>
  <Hero
    eyebrow="Solution · HearthAI"
    title="The discharge moment, made understandable."
    lede="HearthAI turns a diabetic patient's own discharge information into an adaptive, spoken conversation at their reading level — designed to help them retain what they need to do, and to reduce preventable readmissions."
    primaryCta={{ href: "mailto:peresteai@gmail.com", label: "Talk to our team" }}
    secondaryCta={{ href: "/about", label: "About Pereste" }}
    image={{ src: "/images/hearthai-phone.png", alt: "HearthAI conversation interface on a phone" }}
  />

  <Section bordered>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
      <div class="md:col-span-4">
        <p class="eyebrow">The problem</p>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-5">
        <p class="lede">
          Older and rural patients leave the hospital with dense PDFs they
          often cannot parse. Adherence drops, confusion compounds, and
          preventable readmissions follow.
        </p>
        <p class="lede">
          Existing tools either live in the cloud — making them hard to
          deploy in clinical settings — or speak at a single, generic
          reading level that misses the patients most at risk.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section tone="subtle">
    <p class="eyebrow mb-4">Our approach</p>
    <h2 class="max-w-3xl mb-12">
      An adaptive conversation, grounded in the patient's own clinical reality.
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <Card
        eyebrow="Adaptive"
        title="Meets each patient at their reading level."
        icon={{ src: "/images/icon-adaptive.svg", alt: "Adaptive" }}
      >
        HearthAI listens to how a patient speaks and adjusts in real time —
        simpler when needed, more detailed when ready. The same conversation
        works for an 85-year-old in a rural clinic and a younger caregiver.
      </Card>
      <Card
        eyebrow="Grounded"
        title="Speaks to their actual discharge, not generic advice."
        icon={{ src: "/images/icon-grounded.svg", alt: "Grounded" }}
      >
        The system is grounded in the patient's own clinical record, so
        guidance is specific to their diagnosis, medications, and care plan
        — not a generic patient-education page.
      </Card>
      <Card
        eyebrow="On-prem"
        title="Designed for institutional deployment."
        icon={{ src: "/images/icon-onprem.svg", alt: "On-prem" }}
      >
        HearthAI is built to run inside the institutions that care for the
        patient. Patient data stays where it belongs, under the governance
        the institution already trusts.
      </Card>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section bordered>
    <p class="eyebrow mb-4">How a session unfolds</p>
    <h2 class="max-w-3xl mb-12">
      Three moments from a HearthAI conversation.
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-10">
      <div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div
            class="absolute -inset-6 -z-10 rounded-[40px] opacity-60 blur-2xl"
            style="background: radial-gradient(55% 55% at 50% 50%, #C9C7F4 0%, rgba(201,199,244,0) 70%);"
            aria-hidden="true"
          ></div>
          <img
            src="/images/screen-checkin.png"
            alt="Daily check-in screen — How is your blood sugar today, Mary?"
            class="w-full h-auto"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </div>
        <p class="eyebrow mt-6 mb-2">Step one</p>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl tracking-tight-2 mb-2">Check in.</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed">
          A simple, plain-language prompt — at the patient's reading level —
          opens the session.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div
            class="absolute -inset-6 -z-10 rounded-[40px] opacity-60 blur-2xl"
            style="background: radial-gradient(55% 55% at 50% 50%, #C9C7F4 0%, rgba(201,199,244,0) 70%);"
            aria-hidden="true"
          ></div>
          <img
            src="/images/screen-speaking.png"
            alt="Hearth speaking — Take a small juice box, or four glucose tablets"
            class="w-full h-auto"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </div>
        <p class="eyebrow mt-6 mb-2">Step two</p>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl tracking-tight-2 mb-2">Listen along.</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed">
          HearthAI speaks back in clear, specific guidance grounded in the
          patient's own clinical context.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div
            class="absolute -inset-6 -z-10 rounded-[40px] opacity-60 blur-2xl"
            style="background: radial-gradient(55% 55% at 50% 50%, #C9C7F4 0%, rgba(201,199,244,0) 70%);"
            aria-hidden="true"
          ></div>
          <img
            src="/images/screen-detail.png"
            alt="Low blood sugar detail screen with Ask Hearth about this"
            class="w-full h-auto"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </div>
        <p class="eyebrow mt-6 mb-2">Step three</p>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl tracking-tight-2 mb-2">Go deeper.</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed">
          Patients can dive into specific guidance and ask follow-up
          questions in their own words.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section bordered>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
      <div class="md:col-span-4">
        <p class="eyebrow">What it's built for</p>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-5">
        <p class="lede">
          HearthAI starts with diabetic discharge — a population with both
          a strong evidence base for readmission cost and a clear improvement
          loop: better understanding of the discharge plan correlates with
          better adherence and fewer return visits.
        </p>
        <p class="lede">
          The same underlying approach extends to other chronic conditions
          where adherence and understanding drive outcomes — the patient
          population stays the same, the diagnoses change.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
      <div class="md:col-span-4">
        <p class="eyebrow">Where it's heading</p>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-5">
        <p class="lede">
          HearthAI is in active pilot. We're working with care settings ready
          to validate the approach with real patients, in real clinical
          workflows.
        </p>
        <p class="lede">
          If your institution serves patients who would benefit from a more
          adaptive, voice-based handoff at discharge, we'd like to hear
          from you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section>
    <CTA
      eyebrow="For institutions"
      title="Bring HearthAI to your patients."
      body="We partner with health systems and clinical research settings to deploy HearthAI in real care workflows, with no PHI egress and no parallel infrastructure to maintain."
      primaryCta={{ href: "mailto:peresteai@gmail.com", label: "Start the conversation" }}
      tone="ink"
    />
  </Section>
</Base>
